# 詞: 睇怕

1. 佢睇到咁多鬼鬼祟祟嘅人，就睇怕咁，好似見到鬼一樣。 (He got really scared when he saw so many sneaky people, as if he had seen a ghost.)
2. 我哋去鬼屋拍攝，佢一開始都睇怕，但最後都習慣咗。 (We went to a haunted house to film, and he was scared at first, but he got used to it in the end.)
3. 佢睇到蜘蛛就睇怕，都唔敢碰到。 (He gets scared just by seeing spiders and won't even touch them.)
4. 我哋去海邊，佢睇到大魚就睇怕，好似要逃走一樣。 (When we went to the beach, he got scared by seeing big fish and seemed like he wanted to run away.)
5. 佢睇到電影《鬼屋》就睇怕，都唔敢睇完。 (He got scared watching the movie "Haunted House" and couldn't finish it.)
6. 佢睇到黑暗就睇怕，都唔敢自己單獨出街。 (He gets scared of the dark and doesn't dare go out alone.)
7. 佢睇到老鼠就睇怕，都唔敢靠近食物。 (He gets scared of mice and won't even approach food.)
8. 佢睇到高樓就睇怕，都唔敢坐電梯。 (He gets scared of tall buildings and won't even use the elevator.)
9. 佢睇到鬼故事就睇怕，都唔敢睇完。 (He gets scared by ghost stories and won't finish watching them.)
10. 佢睇到大聲嘅雷聲就睇怕，都唔敢出戶。 (He gets scared by loud thunder and won't go out.)
